<br>
Mana song WAY more important then any other song the Bard may sing.<br>
I love it when he sings the offensive songs and Healing etc etc But as a Cleric with 201 Wisdom and + 375 mana I can Watch my mana jump every tick. Fully Buffed my Ogre has just shy of 4000 hit points 3895 to be exact and I won't wear a Fungal Tunic during fights because I lose way to much ac and Stats. So even with Regrowth (witch is 300 mana to cast in the first place) I'd regen at around 17 to 19 per tick. The average mob hitting me hits for 80 to 150. I would MUCH rather the Cleric getting mana fast then an extra 15 hitpoints a tick.<br>
<br>
Yes perhaps if you pull slow enough Regrowth - Bard song and Fungal Tunic would be great but With the casters especially the cleric getting fast mana you can maintain a MUCH faster pull rate. <p><b>Da Rok</b><br>
